    <p>Rules
        <ol>
            <li>
                Only high rollers!
            </li>
            <li>
                Only four cards on the table
            </li>
            <li>
                Score the lowest instead of the highest
            </li>
            <li>
                Same coloured cards count as the same suit
            </li>
        </ol>
    </p>
<p> Special hands!
<ol>
    <li> 
        Weak Flush - A four card flush
    </li>
    <li> 
        Weak Straight - A four card straight
    </li>
    <li> 
        Forgot To Flush - Three red cards and three black cards
    </li>
    <li> 
        Royal Fart - Cards 1, 2, 3, 5, 6, 7 - Three red cards and three black cards
    </li>
</ol>
